factory service provider

factory provider is only avilable in angular 1.

angular2 4 5 6 -- factory provider is deprected only service avilable.

angular framework creates scope and StudentService objects and provide to controller.

StudentService -- Dependency

StudentController -- Dependent



module controller service  $http  ajax 

$http -- ajax calls to the server(rest api)

	get			-- accessing the data
	post		-- send the data for insertion
	put			-- send the data for update
	delete		-- delete the data
	
200 -- success

404 -- not found

500	-- application error

$http.get("url").then(f1,f2);

then provides call back functionality for ajax calls































